    <h1>How Cold Does Kilimanjaro Actually Get?</h1>
    <p>Real temperature ranges on Mount Kilimanjaro by climate zone, why summit night reaches -20 C even at the equator, and what clothing actually keeps you warm.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span>By <a href="/about">Nelson Mushi</a></span>
      <span>&middot; 2026-06-14</span>
      <span>&middot; <a href="/blog">Back to Blog</a></span>
